<directions xmlns:php="http://php.net/xsl">&gt;
<step><![CDATA[soak mushrooms, 25m]]></step>
<step><![CDATA[cut pork into marshmallow sized chunks]]></step>
<step><![CDATA[heat oil in wok, add sugar until reddish]]></step>
<step><![CDATA[add pork and stir well, 4 mÂ ]]></step>
<step><![CDATA[move to pot, add ginger, soy sauce, rice wine until simmering]]></step>
<step><![CDATA[add cinnamon, anise, chestnuts, dried mushrooms, spring onions, hot water, salt, mix]]></step>
<step><![CDATA[lower heat and cover]]></step>
<step><![CDATA[every 5 mins or so, add 3 tbsp water to roasting pork; continue for 1 to 1.5 hrs (or 2 to 2.5 hours if skin is still on)]]></step>
<step><![CDATA[soak noodles in hot water, 20 m, then drain (10) add the noodles to the pot, and keep cooking another 10 m]]></step>
&gt;</directions>
